text: Linda Bengtsson (born 12 February 1988) is a Swedish football defender who currently plays for Djurgårdens IF. She has played Damallsvenskan football for Hammarby IF. ==Career== Bengtsson started her career in Vimmerby IF. During the 2010 and 2011 season, she played for Damallsvenskan side Hammarby IF DFF, where she made a total of nine appearances. ==References== Category:1988 births Category:Living people Category:Swedish women's footballers Category:Hammarby Fotboll (women) players Category:Djurgårdens IF Fotboll (women) players Category:Damallsvenskan players Category:Vimmerby IF players Category:Women's association football defenders
